1
00:00:00,720 --> 00:00:01,960
We're unstoppable!

2
00:00:02,580 --> 00:00:06,840
It's because we're Fairy Tail, see?!

3
00:00:11,600 --> 00:00:15,840
I need to think a bit-kabo...

4
00:00:16,170 --> 00:00:17,910
Alexei-sama...

5
00:00:17,910 --> 00:00:20,750
Here's the list of battle matches...

6
00:00:21,520 --> 00:00:23,470
This match-up...

7
00:00:23,620 --> 00:00:27,080
The management is well-informed.

8
00:00:27,800 --> 00:00:29,910
Shall we begin?

9
00:00:29,910 --> 00:00:33,890
For the sake of our true purpose...

10
00:02:08,750 --> 00:02:10,100
And now, I'll announce

11
00:02:10,100 --> 00:02:14,350
the current standings of the third 
day of the Grand Magic Games!

12
00:02:14,560 --> 00:02:17,860
As before, Raven Tail is in first place!

13
00:02:21,240 --> 00:02:23,860
The time has come at last...

14
00:02:24,650 --> 00:02:27,250
Move out, people.

15
00:02:30,860 --> 00:02:34,140
Still in second place, Lamia Scale!

16
00:02:37,530 --> 00:02:41,170
In third place, one rank down, Sabertooth!

17
00:02:44,880 --> 00:02:47,790
In fourth place, Mermaid Heel!

18
00:02:50,060 --> 00:02:51,580
And tied for fourth,

19
00:02:51,580 --> 00:02:55,470
moving up two ranks, the Fairy Tail A team!

20
00:02:58,340 --> 00:03:00,060
Alright!

21
00:03:00,070 --> 00:03:02,720
We're gonna move up even more ranks!

22
00:03:02,720 --> 00:03:04,750
Aye, sir!

23
00:03:05,200 --> 00:03:08,720
In sixth place, the Fairy Tail B team!

24
00:03:11,160 --> 00:03:13,390
We ain't gonna lose either!

25
00:03:13,810 --> 00:03:15,980
And you can see the last 
place teams for yourself.

26
00:03:17,490 --> 00:03:20,410
I guess when you're in seventh place, 
you don't even get a name check...

27
00:03:20,550 --> 00:03:22,410
Humiliating parfum!

28
00:03:23,610 --> 00:03:27,710
If Quatro Puppy's gonna be our 
name, I'm glad he didn't say it!

29
00:03:29,550 --> 00:03:32,110
Laxus vs. Alexei!

30
00:03:34,600 --> 00:03:39,730
Alright, the battle part of the third day 
of the Grand Magic Games is about to begin!

31
00:03:42,400 --> 00:03:45,220
I'm looking forward to the battle part!

32
00:03:45,220 --> 00:03:46,150
Indeed.

33
00:03:46,970 --> 00:03:50,420
In the first match, it's 
Millianna of Mermaid Heel...

34
00:03:52,800 --> 00:03:56,500
...vs. Semas of Quatro Puppy!

35
00:03:58,900 --> 00:04:01,850
Our souls are always Wild...

36
00:04:01,850 --> 00:04:03,640
...Four!

37
00:04:03,640 --> 00:04:05,860
Let the match begin!

38
00:04:09,270 --> 00:04:11,510
Victory goes to the swiftest!

39
00:04:11,540 --> 00:04:14,390
Wild Spin!

40
00:04:18,170 --> 00:04:22,770
Oh, my! It's a body attack, using 
his giant body to spin around!

41
00:04:23,580 --> 00:04:25,770
I'll use magic to slow him down!

42
00:04:25,770 --> 00:04:27,540
Cat Binding Tube!

43
00:04:30,400 --> 00:04:31,760
It bounced right off!

44
00:04:31,980 --> 00:04:33,180
Millianna!

45
00:04:33,350 --> 00:04:34,510
Attaboy!

46
00:04:34,510 --> 00:04:37,680
Our souls are always Wild...

47
00:04:37,680 --> 00:04:39,080
...Four!

48
00:04:39,080 --> 00:04:41,320
Keep it up and you'll win!

49
00:04:42,180 --> 00:04:43,500
I'm not done yet!

50
00:04:43,500 --> 00:04:46,240
Wild...

51
00:04:46,240 --> 00:04:47,860
Kitten Blast!

52
00:04:51,520 --> 00:04:55,760
That spurred my spinning on 
even more! Now take this!

53
00:04:58,130 --> 00:04:59,710
Beat her with one shot!

54
00:04:59,710 --> 00:05:02,630
Our souls are always Wild...

55
00:05:02,630 --> 00:05:04,210
...Four!

56
00:05:04,210 --> 00:05:07,070
I hope Millianna's okay...

57
00:05:07,120 --> 00:05:09,870
She's taken a lot of damage.

58
00:05:09,880 --> 00:05:10,920
Erza...

59
00:05:10,920 --> 00:05:12,370
She's fine.

60
00:05:13,060 --> 00:05:15,910
Millianna would never lose 
over a few bruises like this.

61
00:05:16,540 --> 00:05:18,150
Millianna!

62
00:05:18,150 --> 00:05:20,040
Hang in there!

63
00:05:20,650 --> 00:05:23,480
There's someone Millianna needs to defeat.

64
00:05:23,980 --> 00:05:26,880
Until she brings him down, she won't lose.

65
00:05:29,380 --> 00:05:32,560
If I can't beat a guy like 
this, I better pack it in...

66
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:35,640
There'd be no point in joining Mermaid Heel!

67
00:05:35,640 --> 00:05:37,400
Time to end this!

68
00:05:37,400 --> 00:05:40,810
Wild Spin, twice as fast!

69
00:05:40,810 --> 00:05:44,190
Uh-oh! Is this gonna decide the match?!

70
00:05:44,190 --> 00:05:46,380
Cat Binding Tube!

71
00:05:47,450 --> 00:05:49,800
I'll tear this junk right off!

72
00:05:49,800 --> 00:05:52,240
I'm not letting go, no matter what!

73
00:06:03,070 --> 00:06:06,950
W-W-Wild...

74
00:06:11,500 --> 00:06:14,360
That ain't wild at all!

75
00:06:16,760 --> 00:06:18,550
Feelin' spiffy!

76
00:06:18,550 --> 00:06:20,970
Semas is down for the count!

77
00:06:20,970 --> 00:06:23,740
The winner is Millianna!

78
00:06:27,000 --> 00:06:31,300
Kagura-chan! Risley-chan! I won!

79
00:06:27,800 --> 00:06:30,320
Now that was an interesting battle!

80
00:06:30,320 --> 00:06:34,320
And she used various kinds of 
magic. I learned something.

81
00:06:34,760 --> 00:06:37,400
You've improved, Millianna.

82
00:06:37,490 --> 00:06:39,470
Even though getting bound by that tube

83
00:06:39,470 --> 00:06:43,010
wouldn't draw a score on that 
magic-measuring device from before...

84
00:06:43,010 --> 00:06:45,370
Bound...?

85
00:06:45,450 --> 00:06:49,090
It was rough for me when I went up 
against her a long time ago, too.

86
00:06:50,280 --> 00:06:52,680
I hate Jellal, too...

87
00:06:55,910 --> 00:06:59,060
Next, the second match for the battle part!

88
00:06:59,100 --> 00:07:02,450
From Sabertooth, the minstrel 
who sings to the red moon...

89
00:07:02,450 --> 00:07:05,060
Rufus Lohr!

90
00:07:09,000 --> 00:07:12,320
Versus Holy Night Eve of Blue Pegasus...

91
00:07:12,320 --> 00:07:14,600
Eve Tilm!

92
00:07:18,840 --> 00:07:21,700
Eve-kun, the parfum of victory!

93
00:07:21,700 --> 00:07:23,030
Do your best!

94
00:07:23,030 --> 00:07:25,190
Fight, Eve!

95
00:07:25,380 --> 00:07:28,000
These two clashed during the 
competition of the first day,

96
00:07:28,000 --> 00:07:31,000
and now they'll collide in 
battle on the third day!

97
00:07:32,800 --> 00:07:35,580
Snow Magic: White Fury!

98
00:07:37,390 --> 00:07:40,280
That's your memory of where I <i>was</i> standing.

99
00:07:41,310 --> 00:07:44,360
I already experienced your 
skill during "Hidden".

100
00:07:44,550 --> 00:07:46,360
And I remember it well!

101
00:07:46,370 --> 00:07:48,960
You remember it, eh?

102
00:07:49,510 --> 00:07:51,280
Eh?

103
00:07:51,760 --> 00:07:54,860
S-Sensei! What are you doing here?!

104
00:07:55,200 --> 00:07:57,280
That's your memory.

105
00:08:01,360 --> 00:08:03,700
Eve's got a memory like that?!

106
00:08:03,700 --> 00:08:06,340
What are you doing, Senpai?!

107
00:08:06,340 --> 00:08:11,630
I don't remember that parfum! Men!

108
00:08:16,140 --> 00:08:18,000
A star falls on the night!

109
00:08:20,180 --> 00:08:22,460
A direct hit on Eve!

110
00:08:23,940 --> 00:08:27,620
Or so we thought, but it was 
just a copy made of snow!

111
00:08:27,950 --> 00:08:29,870
A brilliant parfum!

112
00:08:30,060 --> 00:08:31,430
That's the way, Eve!

113
00:08:31,430 --> 00:08:32,960
Keep it up!

114
00:08:32,960 --> 00:08:36,470
Eve-kun was originally a member 
of the Council, wasn't he?

115
00:08:36,470 --> 00:08:37,680
That's right.

116
00:08:37,720 --> 00:08:42,570
He was a Rune Knight of the Enforcement 
and Detention Corps like the rest of us.

117
00:08:42,810 --> 00:08:46,540
Yes, even back then, he was a shining light,

118
00:08:46,820 --> 00:08:50,810
but after entering a guild, his 
magic has become even more polished.

119
00:08:51,400 --> 00:08:53,150
White Blizzard!

120
00:08:53,430 --> 00:08:55,210
You waste your time.

121
00:08:55,520 --> 00:08:57,610
I don't think so.

122
00:08:57,790 --> 00:09:02,010
I'm using White Blizzard to search 
for the location of your real body!

123
00:09:02,160 --> 00:09:04,710
Over there! White Fang!

124
00:09:06,120 --> 00:09:08,690
I remember that magic.

125
00:09:09,900 --> 00:09:11,800
Memory Make.

126
00:09:12,120 --> 00:09:12,970
There it is...

127
00:09:12,970 --> 00:09:15,920
What kind of Molding Magic is that?!

128
00:09:16,750 --> 00:09:19,600
Magic that gives form to memories?

129
00:09:19,600 --> 00:09:20,910
That's...

130
00:09:21,300 --> 00:09:22,980
...an ancient spell.

131
00:09:23,250 --> 00:09:25,000
In other words, Ancient Magic.

132
00:09:25,000 --> 00:09:29,750
So there's more to this 
than meets the eye, huh?

133
00:09:30,910 --> 00:09:33,740
Oh, boy! W-What is...?

134
00:09:35,130 --> 00:09:37,670
It's getting kind of hot out here...

135
00:09:38,150 --> 00:09:41,200
I'm sensing the rise of a 
tremendous magic power...

136
00:09:53,980 --> 00:09:57,120
Rage of the Burning Earth!

137
00:10:11,820 --> 00:10:14,560
The match is over!

138
00:10:20,400 --> 00:10:25,350
Eve fought a good fight, 
but he fell short of Rufus!

139
00:10:25,500 --> 00:10:28,830
The winner is Rufus of Sabertooth!

140
00:10:28,830 --> 00:10:31,040
He really is strong!

141
00:10:36,520 --> 00:10:38,350
Memory Molding...

142
00:10:39,080 --> 00:10:42,220
It's my job to beat him.

143
00:10:42,970 --> 00:10:46,270
How could Eve lose like that? Crap...

144
00:10:46,800 --> 00:10:49,750
Still, he really did do his best...

145
00:10:49,750 --> 00:10:51,090
Meister...

146
00:10:51,250 --> 00:10:54,180
We've really fallen hard in the rankings...

147
00:10:54,910 --> 00:10:58,870
Like a flower's parfum, be at ease, men.

148
00:11:02,150 --> 00:11:05,330
We still have a secret weapon.

149
00:11:10,830 --> 00:11:12,880
We have a secret weapon.

150
00:11:16,120 --> 00:11:18,880
It's so important that I said it twice.

151
00:11:19,090 --> 00:11:20,590
So we've learned.

152
00:11:24,100 --> 00:11:27,850
At any rate, I wonder who 
that rabbit really is...

153
00:11:27,850 --> 00:11:30,350
If he won't even tell us...

154
00:11:30,350 --> 00:11:33,200
Don't tell me it's not even 
a member of our guild?

155
00:11:33,800 --> 00:11:36,260
That'd be against the rules!

156
00:11:37,810 --> 00:11:42,090
Moving right along, let's 
begin the third match-kabo!

157
00:11:42,690 --> 00:11:47,550
From the Fairy Tail B team, Laxus Dreyar!

158
00:11:49,670 --> 00:11:54,330
Versus Alexei of Raven Tail!

159
00:11:55,990 --> 00:11:57,460
It's Laxus!

160
00:11:57,770 --> 00:11:59,820
His opponent is from Ivan's guild...

161
00:12:00,770 --> 00:12:03,150
Good luck, Laxus!

162
00:12:03,150 --> 00:12:05,650
I'm sure you got nothin' to worry about.

163
00:12:05,860 --> 00:12:07,530
We're talking about Laxus here...

164
00:12:07,530 --> 00:12:11,880
But... Juvia's got a bad feeling about this...

165
00:12:46,750 --> 00:12:51,280
There's been bad blood between father and 
son guilds since day one, right, Yajima-san?

166
00:12:53,070 --> 00:12:57,260
Lahar-kun, you brought along 
people from the Corps, right?

167
00:12:57,870 --> 00:12:59,970
Yes. A few.

168
00:13:00,260 --> 00:13:01,640
Because of regulations...

169
00:13:02,200 --> 00:13:04,940
Keep a close eye on Raven Tail.

170
00:13:04,940 --> 00:13:08,680
If there's any skulduggery, 
stop the match immediately.

171
00:13:09,290 --> 00:13:10,130
Right.

172
00:13:10,910 --> 00:13:12,240
Warren...

173
00:13:12,280 --> 00:13:13,640
Roger!

174
00:13:14,280 --> 00:13:17,080
This is HQ! Bisca, can you hear me?

175
00:13:17,220 --> 00:13:19,870
What do you mean "HQ", Warren?

176
00:13:20,350 --> 00:13:23,400
No movement from Master Ivan. Go ahead.

177
00:13:23,420 --> 00:13:24,490
Roger!

178
00:13:25,060 --> 00:13:27,450
Team Raijinshuu plus Lisanna...

179
00:13:27,500 --> 00:13:28,500
How 'bout you?

180
00:13:28,890 --> 00:13:31,720
This is Raijinshuu plus Lisanna.

181
00:13:31,720 --> 00:13:35,120
Currently, there are no conspicuous 
movements from Raven Tail.

182
00:13:35,220 --> 00:13:38,920
I'm not gonna let you do any funny 
business like that first day, Crow-chan!

183
00:13:38,920 --> 00:13:41,940
Just try to tarnish Laxus's valor.

184
00:13:41,970 --> 00:13:46,510
The Raijinshuu won't guarantee your lives.

185
00:13:47,150 --> 00:13:50,600
Ever says she wants to go back by Elfman...

186
00:13:50,600 --> 00:13:52,280
Please grant her permission.

187
00:13:52,280 --> 00:13:54,120
I said no such thing!

188
00:13:54,740 --> 00:13:56,130
Ivan...

189
00:13:56,200 --> 00:13:59,570
I won't let you pull any 
more cowardly stunts.

190
00:14:01,610 --> 00:14:04,340
Is something wrong, First Master?

191
00:14:04,340 --> 00:14:06,960
No, nothing.

192
00:14:07,850 --> 00:14:11,000
Doing everything in your power 
to protect your comrades...

193
00:14:11,340 --> 00:14:16,170
And just a little bit of 
enjoying the circumstances...

194
00:14:18,300 --> 00:14:19,820
It's splendid.

195
00:14:20,520 --> 00:14:23,330
The ultimate form of my aspirations

196
00:14:24,060 --> 00:14:27,190
is right before my eyes.

197
00:14:28,190 --> 00:14:32,130
Don't forget this, Third Master.

198
00:14:32,130 --> 00:14:34,690
Um... Or is it sixth?

199
00:14:35,710 --> 00:14:37,600
I appreciate the kind words.

200
00:14:37,600 --> 00:14:39,570
And it's actually the seventh...

201
00:14:39,570 --> 00:14:40,880
Sixth is right!

202
00:14:40,880 --> 00:14:42,570
Get a grip!

203
00:14:43,040 --> 00:14:45,270
Both of you, step forward!

204
00:14:49,800 --> 00:14:51,710
Let the match begin!

205
00:14:55,160 --> 00:14:57,390
So you're in my old man's guild?

206
00:14:57,410 --> 00:15:00,060
Who the hell are you, anyway...?

207
00:15:18,240 --> 00:15:19,720
This guy...

208
00:15:27,450 --> 00:15:28,870
How...?

209
00:15:28,870 --> 00:15:30,250
You gotta be kiddin' me!

210
00:15:30,250 --> 00:15:31,700
He's getting his ass kicked?

211
00:15:34,180 --> 00:15:35,940
I don't believe it... Laxus?!

212
00:15:35,940 --> 00:15:38,400
W-What's going on?

213
00:15:38,750 --> 00:15:41,760
Who the hell is that masked freak?!

214
00:15:42,490 --> 00:15:45,050
No way! Laxus...?!

215
00:15:49,070 --> 00:15:52,190
My goodness... Alexei keeps pouring it on!

216
00:15:52,190 --> 00:15:54,850
Laxus can't even lift a finger!

217
00:16:09,080 --> 00:16:11,430
What the hell is this?

218
00:16:12,260 --> 00:16:15,030
A kind of Hallucination Magic.

219
00:16:15,220 --> 00:16:17,130
Everyone around us

220
00:16:17,130 --> 00:16:21,350
is talking about this right now. 
They can't see our true bodies.

221
00:16:21,350 --> 00:16:23,440
They can't hear us either.

222
00:16:24,680 --> 00:16:28,330
What they see are phantoms fighting.

223
00:16:32,750 --> 00:16:34,880
It looks real, doesn't it?

224
00:16:34,880 --> 00:16:37,600
Not one person realizes it's an illusion.

225
00:16:38,030 --> 00:16:43,040
The crowd is watching images of the 
mighty Laxus as helpless as a baby.

226
00:16:43,190 --> 00:16:46,660
Why is Laxus on the ropes like this?!

227
00:16:46,700 --> 00:16:47,750
Bisca!

228
00:16:48,000 --> 00:16:49,740
Ivan isn't doing anything!

229
00:16:49,750 --> 00:16:51,930
Raijinshuu plus Lisanna!

230
00:16:52,060 --> 00:16:54,950
I don't think they're doing 
anything crooked over here either!

231
00:16:54,950 --> 00:16:59,100
This is unbelievable! Laxus! 
It's time to get serious!

232
00:16:59,100 --> 00:17:00,510
Dammit...

233
00:17:02,040 --> 00:17:04,830
Laxus! What's wrong?!

234
00:17:05,550 --> 00:17:08,830
It seems that even your guild idolizes you.

235
00:17:11,490 --> 00:17:15,930
I wonder how your compatriots 
feel while watching this...

236
00:17:16,410 --> 00:17:17,470
Laxus!

237
00:17:19,380 --> 00:17:20,850
Hey, come on...

238
00:17:20,850 --> 00:17:23,100
I've got no idea what this is about.

239
00:17:23,580 --> 00:17:24,760
About?

240
00:17:25,300 --> 00:17:29,760
What's the point of 
winning an illusory battle?

241
00:17:30,190 --> 00:17:31,780
Exactly.

242
00:17:32,040 --> 00:17:35,110
Our goal isn't "victory".

243
00:17:35,430 --> 00:17:38,970
This hallucination is just camouflage.

244
00:17:40,470 --> 00:17:42,380
An illusion is an illusion.

245
00:17:43,850 --> 00:17:46,840
The end result can be altered as we like.

246
00:17:47,110 --> 00:17:49,680
End result, you say?

247
00:17:49,800 --> 00:17:51,370
Laxus!

248
00:17:51,660 --> 00:17:53,770
Go, Laxus!

249
00:17:53,850 --> 00:17:55,120
Hang in there!

250
00:18:08,350 --> 00:18:12,280
Oh, my! Laxus has begun to counterattack!

251
00:18:25,640 --> 00:18:28,950
That's how you do it! Go, Laxus!

252
00:18:25,770 --> 00:18:28,550
Go! Do your best!

253
00:18:30,660 --> 00:18:32,600
Alright! Go!

254
00:18:32,600 --> 00:18:34,120
Easy win!

255
00:18:35,860 --> 00:18:37,870
I figured he'd be okay.

256
00:18:37,870 --> 00:18:39,120
Yeah...

257
00:18:45,730 --> 00:18:48,340
Yes! That ought to settle it!

258
00:18:46,110 --> 00:18:47,740
Yeah!

259
00:18:48,740 --> 00:18:51,180
It looks like we were worried for nothing.

260
00:18:51,180 --> 00:18:52,030
Warren!

261
00:18:52,030 --> 00:18:53,160
Right!

262
00:18:53,900 --> 00:18:55,960
Good job, Bisca.

263
00:18:55,960 --> 00:18:56,990
Thanks.

264
00:18:57,240 --> 00:18:59,550
Raijinshuu plus Lisanna...

265
00:18:59,550 --> 00:19:01,570
In the end, they didn't do anything, huh?

266
00:19:01,750 --> 00:19:05,460
I was a fool for worrying 
about Laxus even for a moment!

267
00:19:18,200 --> 00:19:19,600
What?!

268
00:19:19,600 --> 00:19:21,540
Laxus!

269
00:19:21,540 --> 00:19:24,700
Uh-oh! The tables are turned again!

270
00:19:24,700 --> 00:19:27,710
Is this the end of Laxus's counterattack?!

271
00:19:27,710 --> 00:19:29,260
Laxus!

272
00:19:29,260 --> 00:19:31,380
What the hell is going on here?!

273
00:19:39,180 --> 00:19:42,630
Is this the "end result" 
you were talkin' about?

274
00:19:42,960 --> 00:19:45,560
Depending on your negotiations with us,

275
00:19:45,560 --> 00:19:49,650
it's possible that we would 
even let you win this.

276
00:19:50,600 --> 00:19:52,790
We've got nothing to talk about.

277
00:19:53,620 --> 00:19:56,320
The illusions don't mean a damn thing.

278
00:19:57,130 --> 00:20:01,130
I'm gonna finish this by taking out 
your real self right here and now.

279
00:20:01,340 --> 00:20:03,790
That's impossible!

280
00:20:07,880 --> 00:20:10,640
Reality is harsh.

281
00:20:11,100 --> 00:20:17,120
Not even you can defeat Raven 
Tail's elite all at the same time.

282
00:20:22,850 --> 00:20:25,300
And there's one more thing.

283
00:20:27,000 --> 00:20:30,180
You know how strong I am, don't you...

284
00:20:30,450 --> 00:20:32,280
...my foolish son?

285
00:20:33,220 --> 00:20:36,030
I figured as much...

286
00:20:37,050 --> 00:20:38,590
...useless old man!

287
00:20:39,950 --> 00:20:43,280
Makarov would die before he coughed it up.

288
00:20:53,980 --> 00:20:56,100
But you're different.

289
00:20:57,230 --> 00:20:59,490
Would you tell us?

290
00:21:00,300 --> 00:21:03,230
The location of Lumen Histoire!

291
00:21:03,950 --> 00:21:05,720
What are you talking about?

292
00:21:06,460 --> 00:21:08,600
You don't have to play dumb.

293
00:21:10,100 --> 00:21:13,610
I'm sure Makarov has told you.

294
00:21:13,940 --> 00:21:16,320
Actually, I don't know.

295
00:21:16,630 --> 00:21:19,070
No. You must know.

296
00:21:19,210 --> 00:21:23,570
Well, even if I did, I wouldn't tell you.

297
00:21:24,320 --> 00:21:25,640
Come, come...

298
00:21:25,700 --> 00:21:30,850
You're in a hopeless situation, 
but I'm willing to let you win.

299
00:21:31,360 --> 00:21:35,270
Although if you don't accept the condition...

300
00:21:35,450 --> 00:21:38,800
...it's not going to end with just 
your illusory self being beaten.

301
00:21:40,720 --> 00:21:43,960
Jeez, you're a real pain in the ass.

302
00:21:44,820 --> 00:21:48,260
I can understand why Gramps 
washed his hands of you.

303
00:21:48,630 --> 00:21:50,860
Bring it on.

304
00:21:51,370 --> 00:21:55,220
See, the master's enemies are my enemies!

305
00:21:56,550 --> 00:22:00,350
Apparently, you need to be taught a lesson...

306
00:22:00,690 --> 00:22:07,390
...about the power of Raven Tail,
 the anti-Fairy Tail guild!

307
00:23:56,200 --> 00:23:58,070
What happened to Laxus?!

308
00:23:58,070 --> 00:24:00,570
Those guys aren't using another 
underhanded trick, are they?

309
00:24:00,570 --> 00:24:02,250
Everyone's keepin' a close watch 
on them, so it's gotta be okay.

310
00:24:02,250 --> 00:24:05,060
Maybe he feels really sick...

311
00:24:05,060 --> 00:24:07,450
Like he ate too much at last night's 
banquet and now his stomach is upset?

312
00:24:07,450 --> 00:24:09,060
Or he drank too much...

313
00:24:09,060 --> 00:24:10,580
I bet there's somethin' on his mind!

314
00:24:10,580 --> 00:24:13,440
Like he's lonely 'cause he's
 got almost no friends...

315
00:24:13,870 --> 00:24:16,660
Next time: Wendy vs. Cheria!

316
00:24:16,820 --> 00:24:18,350
I know what it is!

317
00:24:18,350 --> 00:24:19,250
What?

318
00:24:19,250 --> 00:24:21,050
He must be exhausted...

319
00:24:21,050 --> 00:24:22,650
...from listening to your dumb babble!

320
00:24:22,650 --> 00:24:25,110


